2.title: La Esperanza Potosi Sidra Natural
2.about: Sidra from La Esperanza Potosi took the world stage by a storm, as the 2023 World Brewers Cup Champion, Carlos Medina representing Chile used Sidra Natural from La Esperanza Potosi!This lot is from the same farm, same process, but is a different lot. Nevertheless, it is still a very high quality coffee that is rare and exotic

3.title: La Esperanza Cerro Azul Geisha Washed 100 g.
3.about: La Esperanza took the world stage by a storm, as the 2023 World Brewers Cup Champion, Carlos Medina representing Chile used a coffee from La Esperanza!This Geisha from Cerro Azul is a rare and exotic bean that exhibits very traditional Geisha qualities of Floral, Stonefruits.

4.title: Sweet Berry Blend 150 g. [Omni Roast]
4.about: Introducing our - a delightful coffee that will awaken your taste buds with its sweet and tangy flavors of strawberry yogurt. This blend is versatile and suitable for both espresso and pour over methods, making it perfect for any coffee lover.
